text: Kouk Pou Commune () is a khum (commune) in Bourei Cholsar District, Takéo Province, Cambodia. == Administration == As of 2019, Kouk Pou Commune has 8 phums (villages) as follows. {| class="wikitable sortable mw-collapsible" !No. !Code !Village !Khmer |- !1 |21030501 |Kandaol |កណ្ដោល |- !2 |21030502 |Pong Tuek |ពងទឹក |- !3 |21030503 |Chrey Kouk Pou |ជ្រៃគោកពោធិ៍ |- !4 |21030504 |Prey Mul |ព្រៃមូល |- !5 |21030505 |Prey Hiev |ព្រៃហៀវ |- !6 |21030506 |Neak Ta Tbal |អ្នកតាត្បាល់ |- !7 |21030507 |Kampong Youl |កំពង់យោល |- !8 |21030508 |Thma Sa |ថ្មស |} == References == Category:Communes of Takeo Province Category:Bourei Cholsar District
